               <head>Otsrot Ḥayim by Ḥayyim Vital</head>
               
               
               
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85018546" rend="visible">
                  
                  
                  
                  <summary>A kabbalistic treatise edited by Ḥayim Vital, with additions by other kabbalists.</summary>
                  
                  
                  
                  <textLang mainLang="he"/>
                  
                  
                  
                  <msItem rend="">
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Otsrot Ḥayim </title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">אוצרות חיים</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Contains additions and glosses by Moses ben Mordecai Zacuto (marked as Kol Rama"z), Beyamin ha-Kohen and Nathan ben Reuben Shapira. The heading on folio 1 suggest that the work was written by a student of Nathan Shapira.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Prefixed are: Madregot Shem, folios 1v-2r; Moses Zacuto's note on the ten sefirot, folio 2v; Seder ha-orot, folios 3v-4r; Ilan sefirot, folios 5v-6r; Arikh anpin, folio 7r; responsa of Moses Zacuto, folios 8r-23v. </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Appended are additional teachings from the school of Ḥayim Vital, folios 168r-181v. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <locus from="1r" to="181v"/>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/34704971">Vital, Ḥayyim ben Joseph </persName>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="he" key="viaf.org/viaf/34704971">ויטל, חיים בן יוסף </persName>
                     
                     
                     
                     </author>
                     
                     
                     
                     <listBibl>
                        
                        
                        
                        <bibl>
                           
                           
                           
                           <ref target="Otsrot_Hayim_1783"/>
                        
                        
                        
                        </bibl>
                     
                     
                     
                     </listBibl>
                     
                     
                     
                     <filiation>Cf. the same work in Add MS 27066. </filiation>
                     
                     
                     
                     <decoNote type="diagram">
                        
                        
                        
                        <locus from="2v" to="7r"/>Diagrams, in pen and ink. </decoNote>
                  
                  
                  
                  </msItem>
               
               
               
